      "message": "[🟡 Suggestions] Line 478: The announce path emits `SwarmMessageUpdated` for every edit even though `handleEdition()` previously emitted the update only when the parent was changed. Because this loop also runs for commits loaded from history, clients may receive update signals for historical edits during loading/replay, not just new live edits. Gate this emission on the same \u0027message received/live commit\u0027 condition used elsewhere, or ensure history loading cannot reach this announce path.",
