      "message": "[🟡 Suggestions] Line 2046: `loadMissingBodyOverwrites()` treats absence of `bodyOverwrite` as \u0027not processed\u0027. If a plugin legitimately decides there is no overwrite, this method will re-run the plugin transform every time the conversation is loaded, creating avoidable repeated work for every unmodified text message. Store an explicit processed marker in local plugin data, or batch/mark negative results so messages that do not need an overwrite are not transformed repeatedly.",
